<informationtext name="Information">
<![CDATA[
<p>The Community &amp; Regional Development Program (Department of Human Ecology) offers a minor in <span class="title-main">Community Development</span>.</p>
<h2>Minor Advisor</h2>
<p>Jonathan London; see academic advisor <a href="mailto:gerdman@ucdavis.edu" target="_blank">Galyna Erdman</a> in 1331 Hart Hall.</p>
]]>
